data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath brick home that offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, & outdoor enjoyment. The inviting curb appeal of the property features a classic brick façade & matching fence to complete the front of the home. Situated on a large lot with trees providing shade & privacy. Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by a warm & welcoming interior. The spacious living room boasts tall ceilings & ample space. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, & plenty of cabinet space. The home offers 3 bedrooms & a guest bathroom. The primary bedroom is a retreat in itself, with its own bathroom featuring a separate tub & shower. Step outside to your own paradise with the centerpiece being a sparkling pool. A spacious deck & patio area provide ample room for outdoor dining & lounging complete with an outdoor kitchen & fireplace. This property is conveniently close to shopping, dining, & schools.
